00:42:08,792 --> 00:42:10,885
And you live together?

260
00:42:15,866 --> 00:42:18,061
What are you holding back, Gina?

261
00:42:19,203 --> 00:42:20,693
Tell me what's wrong.

262
00:42:24,208 --> 00:42:26,972
