00:52:26,409 --> 00:52:29,867
And you... you just ignored me.

337
00:52:29,946 --> 00:52:32,437
Mary, I've been here all day.

338
00:52:32,516 --> 00:52:35,041
I didn't go out for lunch.

339
00:52:35,118 --> 00:52:37,518
I could have sworn I...

